# $Id: AnimeNoTomodachi,v 1.3 2004-03-13 16:02:31 mitch Exp $
#
# Anime no Tomodachi style for the Fluxbox window manager
#
# 2004 by Christian Garbs <mitch@tomodachi.de>
#
# This style is designed to match the layouts from
# http://anime.no.tomodachi.de and http://forum.tomodachi.de
#
# I started hacking with "Mereley Kay" (shipped with fluxbox) as a
# template, but none of the original settings should have survived.

